{"type": "article", "id": 14414, "title": "挂在树上的灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-04T07:39:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000317X9i85MaBsEIbwCZH.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这盏挂在植物上的灯，专门帮助常年不见阳光的小型盆栽进行光合作用。出自意大利设计师 Lorenzo Antonioni 之手，小巧的陶制灯罩富有艺术感，与绿色植物之间构成微妙而柔和的对比，光照之余，也能充当房间的装饰品。这盏灯可以插上铝棍直接放在盆栽里，也可以吊起来。灯泡统一为 7W，可以选择红色或灰色的灯线，售价 119 欧。<a href=\"http://www.crowdyhouse.com/shop/cynara-pottery-led-grow-light/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141951sNq0HTr2vQZF53d8.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"431\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.45851064\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141951KaC1HsuXjcgJrfvt.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"431\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.45851064\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261419510imcwWfN9nOjKIDy.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"587\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.62446809\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141952KHLJmWwFcR8reGbE.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"567\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.60319149\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}